                                    <div id="aboutUs" >
                                        <div class="content_heading">
                                            <div class="heading"><h2>About</h2> </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <p>MR DAV Institute of Management Studies, a premier Institute of learning in Management and Computer Applications was established in the year 1998. The campus is spread over 7 acres of land at 5 Km Stone, Sonepat Road, Rohtak well connected with rail & road transport. MR DAV IMS is approved by All India Council of Technical Education (AICTE), Govt. of India, State Govt. of Haryana & affiliated to M.D. University, Rohtak. The Institute is run & managed by Association of Persons known as MR DAV Educational Trust.</p>
                                        <br />
                                        <p>Ever since, MR DAV IMS was born, it has been growing at a path-breaking pace due to the visionary outlook of our Director, Professor Shiv Kumar Jindal and the dynamic leadership of the Principal, Professor Surender Kumar Shilla along with the dedicated and able faculty members. The Institute is presently running MBA & MCA Programs. Over the last 10 years MR DAVians consistently have shown achievements in both academics and corporate sectors, which are unparalleled in the history of any academic institution.</p>
                                        <br />    
                                        <p>The apex rating agency of the repute “All India Management Association” (AIMA) has rated MR DAV IMS, Rohtak as “A Category Business School”. In fact, it is the only institute in the State of Haryana being rated as “Category A” Business School.</p>
                                        <br /><br />
                                    </div>

                                    <div id="vision">
                                        <div class="content_heading">
                                            <div class="heading"><h2>Our Vision</h2> </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <p>The Vision of MR DAV Institute of Management Studies, Rohtak is to make it an internationally accepted Centre of excellence in Management and Information Technology.</p>
                                        <br /><br />
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div id="mission">
                                        <div class="content_heading">
                                            <div class="heading"><h2>Our Mission</h2> </div>
                                        </div>

                                        <p>The Institute endures to imbibe in each of its fraternity the ideals of our mission “Always Ahead”. We are committed to continuous improvement in the quality of education by designing & maintaining an environment, which will contributes towards the enhancement in employability & place ability of student. We give lot of importance to honing their emotional intelligence, intuition, which are transformational in nature of effect a paradigm shift, thus shaping original inspiring performer motivated by conscience, conviction, owning responsibility & following right means to be “Always Ahead”.</p>
   
                                        <br /><br />
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="cpm">
                                        <div class="content_heading">
                                            <div class="heading"><h2>Chairperson's Message</h2> </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <img alt="" style="width:760px" src="DynamicImages/ImageRecord/PersonImage/chairperson.jpg" /><br /><br/>
                                            <span style="font-size:14px"><b>Mrs. Geeta Jindal</b></span><br /><br />
                                        <p>The worth encouraging developments in the management education are the burgeoning global demand for techno-managers. MR DAV IMS has made a target to equip students of the Institution of the foundation, so that they excel in their life to achieve all their goals.</p>
                                        <br />
                                        <p>I am pleased and highly impressed that MR DAV IMS, Rohtak is striving continuously for excellence, which resulted in “Catego¬ry-A” Business School as per the “Best Business School” survey 2008 conducted by AIMA, which truly justify its mission of “Always Ahead”.</p>
                                        <br />
                                        <p>To all corporate, I extend worm welcome to visit the Institute in its ultra-modern campus at Rohtak. Let us resolve to break the frontiers in education and join hands for selecting the budding managers to best suit your organization.
                                            </p><br /><p>Wishing you all the best.</p>
   
                                        <br /><br />
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="dm">
                                        <div class="content_heading">
                                            <div class="heading"><h2>Director's Message</h2> </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <img alt="" style="width:760px" src="DynamicImages/ImageRecord/PersonImage/director.jpg" /><br /><br/>
                                            <span style="font-size:14px"><b>Prof. Shiv Kumar Jindal</b></span><br /><br />
                                        <p>Almost all organizations throughout the developing world and especially India, are presently going through an introspection phase in the changing business scenario. This change unwinds plenty of opportunities and challenges contributing towards personal and professional development in existing and future Executive/Managers.</p>
                                        <br />
                                        <p> Today, whole world is a common global village facing neck to neck competition for creating company’s brand image. To cope with these challenges, corporate sector demands highly shelled profes¬sionals with multi-faceted competencies.</p>
                                        <br />
                                        <p> Justifying to the current corporate expectation and the “Mission - Always Ahead” the students of MR DAV IMS regularly proving their excellence in the academics and corporate time to time. This year too, the top line rankers in the examination results declared by MDU, Rohtak In August 2008 are MR DAVians. Further adding feather in its cap, MR DAV IMS is continuing its unblem¬ished enviable record of achieving the status of only A-Category.</p>
                                        <br />
                                        <p> I appreciate the commitment & dedication of students and the faculty teams as their joint efforts have initiated a trend of creating performers in MR DAV IMS, Rohtak. The potential managers from MR DAV are competent enough to accept the challenges and to meet the corporate expectations. On behalf of our training and Placement Cell, I look forward to establish a mutually rewarding relationship with your esteemed organization. I cordially extend my invitation for the participation of your company for MR DAV IMS “Campus Placement Week”.</p>
                                        <br /><br />
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="pm">
                                        <div class="content_heading">
                                            <div class="heading"><h2>Principal's Message</h2> </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <img alt="" style="width:760px" src="DynamicImages/ImageRecord/PersonImage/principal.jpg" /><br /><br/>
                                            <span style="font-size:14px"><b>Prof. Surender K. Shilla</b></span><br /><br />
                                        <p>It is my privilege to invite you to the ultra-modern campus of MR DAV IMS, Rohtak for executive placements of our 11th Batch of MBA & 10th Batch of MCA students. MR DAV IMS, Rohtak over the years, has developed the system to groom its students in a manner that they put a step forward for meeting the industry challenges.</p>
                                        <br />
                                        <p> At MR DAV IMS, we believe in delivering more than skills as our training programs are aimed at creating quality professionals. We focus on overall development of character, Skills, Attitude and Personality of Future Professionals. To unleash the potential of nation builders tomorrow, the institute regularly organizes various events to give them flip in practical exposure and build an industry - academia interface.</p>
                                        <br />
                                        <p> Faculty, alertly to fast changing economic & technological envi¬ronment not only updates its curriculum, but also adopt the modern interactive techniques for transfer and diffusion of skills to their students. I congratulate everyone of MR DAV IMS fraternity for their tireless efforts and hope that in future, they would bring more appreciation to the Institute. I cordially invite all the organizations being facilitated by the MR DAV IMS for campus recruitment drive. MR DAVians will prove the best of their potential aligning their individual roles to the strategic goals of your organization.</p>
